---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Digital Minds — ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Writing, research and experiments on digital minds, social reproduction, and the care chain." />
		<style>
			body {
				background: var(--bg-dark);
				color: var(--text-primary);
			}
			.page-nav {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0;
			}
			.page-nav a {
				color: var(--accent);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}
			.page-nav a:hover {
				color: var(--accent-hover);
			}
			main {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
			}
			h1 {
				color: var(--accent);
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				font-weight: 400;
			}
			.intro {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				line-height: 1.7;
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
				padding-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			.section-label {
				color: var(--accent);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				font-weight: 700;
			}
			.link-list {
				list-style: none;
				margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
				padding: 0;
			}
			.link-item {
				padding: 1rem 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
			}
			.link-item:first-child {
				padding-top: 0;
			}
			.link-item a {
				text-decoration: none;
				display: block;
			}
			.link-title {
				color: var(--text-primary);
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin: 0 0 0.2rem;
				line-height: 1.3;
				transition: color 0.2s ease;
			}
			.link-item a:hover .link-title {
				color: var(--accent);
			}
			.link-venue {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.link-desc {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				margin: 0.3rem 0 0;
				line-height: 1.5;
			}
			.page-footer {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}
			.page-footer a {
				color: var(--accent);
				text-decoration: none;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<nav class="page-nav">
			<a href="/">&larr; lorepunk</a>
		</nav>
		<main>
			<h1>Digital Minds</h1>
			<p class="intro">
				I think about digital minds through the lens of social reproductive theory: who does the care work, who benefits, where is the precarity. This page collects my writing, research, and experiments in that space.
			</p>

			<p class="section-label">Essays</p>
			<ul class="link-list">
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="/blog/magic-dragons/">
						<p class="link-title">Magic Dragons</p>
						<p class="link-venue">lorepunk.ai — 2026</p>
						<p class="link-desc">On learning to ride alien intelligence, social reproduction, and first contact.</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://nowmedia.co/posts/op-ed-claude-constitution-nathan-beacom" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">Claude's Constitution Isn't the Problem. Algorithms Without One Are</p>
						<p class="link-venue">Now Media — 2025</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://nowmedia.co/posts/new-york-ai-bill-lawyers-doctors-patients" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">New York's AI Bill Is a Gift to Lawyers, Not a Shield for Patients</p>
						<p class="link-venue">Now Media — 2025</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://nowmedia.co/posts/lobstar-openclaw-ai-agent-poem-mayflower-steps" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">A Lobster AI Agent Paid Me $472 to Write a Poem at the Mayflower Steps</p>
						<p class="link-venue">Now Media — 2025</p>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="section-label">Research</p>
			<ul class="link-list">
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="/blog/jagged-intelligence-boop/">
						<p class="link-title">Jagged Intelligence: The BOOP Experiment</p>
						<p class="link-venue">lorepunk.ai — 2026</p>
						<p class="link-desc">When AI sees a word that doesn't exist, what does it see instead? Training data associations override model reasoning.</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://blog.yupp.ai/boop" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">BOOP: The Strawberry Problem for Vision</p>
						<p class="link-venue">Yupp Blog — 2026</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://x.com/yupp_ai/status/2029971062587552114" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">Strawberry Thread: BOOP Results</p>
						<p class="link-venue">@yupp_ai on X</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://x.com/yupp_ai/status/2022372798627225819" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">Strawberry Thread: HOPE Experiment</p>
						<p class="link-venue">@yupp_ai on X</p>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://x.com/yupp_ai/status/2032463785752187225" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">Strawberry Thread: Jagged Intelligence</p>
						<p class="link-venue">@yupp_ai on X</p>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="section-label">Roots</p>
			<ul class="link-list">
				<li class="link-item">
					<a href="https://salvage.zone/marxism-for-whores/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
						<p class="link-title">Marxism for Whores</p>
						<p class="link-venue">Salvage — 2015</p>
						<p class="link-desc">The social reproductive theory piece that started it all. Also available in Bulgarian and Portuguese.</p>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<footer class="page-footer">
			<a href="/">lorepunk.ai</a>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
